{
  "text": "Each of the previous muon decay global analyses [4, 9, [CITATION_1] 11] utilized the same input parameters -\u03c1, \u03b4, P \u00b5 \u03be\u03b4/\u03c1, \u03be \u2032 , \u03be \u2032\u2032 , \u03b1/A, \u03b2/A, \u03b1 \u2032 /A, \u03b2 \u2032 /A. For each of these quantities, the previous analyses adopted the single most precise experimental measurement that was available at the time.",
